Class HtmlLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • proto.logger.HtmlLogger

  • public class HtmlLogger
extends Object
    This is the html logger which is used for debugging and storing the results of the analysis in the forms of questions and answers. Created by bradlee sargent on 3/22/2019
